title: Gibson Exhaust on 2015 Mustang GT 5.0L with Dyno Run
description:
Stainless System, Part # 619013  //  Elite Black Ceramic, Part # 619013-B

Dyno Graph:
http://gibsonperformance.com/products/retail_prod_annoucement.php?product_number=619013-B

Dyno tested to:
32 hp gain @ 6500 rpm
34 ft-lbs gain @ 4000 rpm

Gibson Performance introduces a new Dual Exhaust system to give the redesigned 6th Generation 2015 Ford Mustang 5.0 steed an extra shot of American-Made power, combined with an aggressive sound that lets others know to take notice.
  
The complete Dual 3” Stainless Steel X Pipe and trusted, power-proven SuperFlow mufflers with integrated CFT technology will create symphony under the chassis, as they work in tune to push any driver deeper into their seat.  With each rap of the throttle, the throaty sound exiting from the Dual 4.5” Intercooled Stainless Tips will work to alter their ego from Office Clerk to Road Warrior.

Choosing between Raw Stainless or Elite Black Ceramic finishes could take longer than installing this Gibson Direct-Fit bolt-on exhaust system, allowing more time to burn fuel and lay rubber. To top it off, the Gibson craftsmen in Corona, California will back this American-Made exhaust system with a Lifetime Limited Warranty to ensure satisfaction is guaranteed.
tags: Gibson Performance Exhaust, Gibson Exhaust Systems, 2015 Ford Mustang GT, dyno, gibson 619013
